---
title: Spiced Veggie & Lentil Israeli Couscous with Herby Apricot Yoghurt
description: We love the tender texture of Israeli (pearl) couscous, each grain holds its shape and it easily handles bold flavours. Combine that
with spiced and roasted veggies, creamy yoghurt and fresh parsley and this is a bowl to remember!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-spiced-veggie-lentil-israeli-couscous-038f41c2.jpg
